data.description: This 3 bed/ 1 bath home has been well maintained and has lots up upgrades which includes a new roof, new windows, tankless water heater and new electric wiring. There is a new concrete driveway with carport.  This home has original charm as well.  You will love the hardwood floors!  Don't miss out on this nice home! Less than 10 miles from Okmulgee Lake!
